---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)] mt-24 bg-[color:var(--color-canvas-warm)]">
  <div class="wrap py-12 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-4">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
        <span class="font-display text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">El Tianguis</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)]">
          por Sistemia
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        El primer tianguis de skills para Claude Code en español. Curado para devs de México y Latinoamérica.
        100% gratis, sin paywalls, sin almacenamiento centralizado — cada skill vive en su repo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)] mb-3">
        Explorar
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Todos los skills</a></li>
        <li><a href="/c/mx-latam" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">MX/Latam</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guia" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Guías</a></li>
        <li><a href="/empezar" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Empezar</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)] mb-3">
        Comunidad
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/publica" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Publica tu skill</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://sistemia.mx" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Sistemia.mx</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)]">
    <div class="wrap py-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3 text-xs text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)]">
      <div>© {year} Sistemia. Hecho en México, abierto a Latinoamérica.</div>
      <div class="font-mono tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">v0.1 · beta abierta</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
